SUMMARY:HLS Fall 2026 Internship: Info Session
DESCRIPTION:Interested in having an internship during the fall semester? 
 Start here!  Our Internship Placement Program offers HLS students an unpa
 ralleled opportunity to gain hands-on professional experience and prepare
  for global careers. HLS will match you with domestic\, remote\, and inte
 rnational internships for the fall\, spring or summer!Fall applications d
 ue April 1  For more information and to apply\, visit our Internship Plac
 ement Program page: https://hls.indiana.edu/careers/internships/internshi
 p-placement-program.html (https://hls.indiana.edu/careers/internships/int
 ernship-placement-program.html)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Interested in having an internship duri
 ng the fall semester? Start here!</p><p>  Our Internship Placement Progra
 m offers HLS students an unparalleled opportunity to gain hands-on profes
 sional experience and prepare for global careers. HLS will match you with
  domestic\, remote\, and international internships for the fall\, spring 
 or summer!</p><p><strong>Fall applications due April 1</strong></p><p>  F
 or more information and to apply\, visit our Internship Placement Program
  page: <a class="external" href="https://hls.indiana.edu/careers/internsh
 ips/internship-placement-program.html">https://hls.indiana.edu/careers/in
 ternships/internship-placement-program.html</a></p>
