 privacy-enhancing free software\, such as <a href="http://trackmenot.io/"
  target="_blank" rel="noopener">TrackMeNot</a> (designed to prevent the p
 rofiling of web search histories) and <a href="https://adnauseam.io/" tar
 get="_blank" rel="noopener">AdNauseam</a> (designed to counter profiling 
 based on ad clicks). She holds a Ph.D. in philosophy from Stanford Univer
